data.description: Welcome to this delightful and well maintained CBS home with 1,582 square feet of comfortable living space, featuring 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and a garage. The kitchen offers ample countertop space with a view of the fenced in backyard. One of the highlights of this home is the spacious, insulated and air conditioned Florida room, providing a comfortable place where you can enjoy the beautiful Florida weather year-round. The property features full pour tie beam construction, ensuring durability and stability for years to come. Situated within walking distance from Sportsman Park, which will offer easy access to recreational activities such as walking trails, playgrounds, and sports facilities. This home offers the perfect blend of comfort, functionality, and convenience.
